{"tid":135751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[COYS - 無咗Kane無得傾] 熱刺球迷吹水區 07","createTime":"2017-02-26T14:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T14:34:52.000Z","uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8f8b4136f2fd4e747692882115f34666a1757a","tid":135751,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/797/Oyk0dK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F797%2FOyk0dK.gif&h=edd86a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">C</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OME</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">O</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">N</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Y</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OU</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>S</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">PURS</span></span><img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/797/Oyk0dK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F797%2FOyk0dK.gif&h=edd86a2d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://sites.psu.edu/natecaseeplweekly/wp-content/uploads/sites/5070/2013/09/White-Hart-Lane.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.psu.edu%2Fnatecaseeplweekly%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F5070%2F2013%2F09%2FWhite-Hart-Lane.jpg&h=b0fe3436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熱刺</span></span></strong>是一間座落倫敦北部托特納姆區的英國職業足球球會<br />\n從1882年成立至今已經擁有過百年歷史，現時競逐於英格蘭超級聯賽；<br />\n球會主場為白鹿徑球場，球會的拉丁文格言「<em>Audere est Facere</em>」則意謂「<em>敢作敢為</em>」</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C3RCvBNWcAIJfm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC3RCvBNWcAIJfm1.jpg&h=0182e3d4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">榮耀:</div></strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">歐洲足協杯 冠軍 : 1972年、1984年<br />\n歐洲盃賽冠軍盃 冠軍 : 1963年<br />\n足總盃 冠軍\t : 1901年、1921年、1961年、1962年、1967年、1981年、1982年、1991年<br />\n聯賽盃 冠軍\t : 1971年、1973年、1999年、2008年</div>"},{"pid":"36c34371e53bbdec5d5a448833b85d9baea16da2","tid":135751,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"出巨巨喇！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b9e2aba844cecee885fdf4cddf3d876d7d2030","tid":135751,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>2016/2017主要職球員</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　　　<strong>Manager</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://bit.ly/19c2sp6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F19c2sp6&h=73eacc20&s={SIZE}\" /> - Mauricio POCHETTINO<br />\n<br />\n　　　　<strong>Goalkeepers</strong><br />\n01 - <img src=\"http://bit.ly/1ftbnaq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1ftbnaq&h=6fa15cf1&s={SIZE}\" /> - Hugo LLORIS (captain)<br />\n13 - <img src=\"http://bit.ly/1jWoN5K\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1jWoN5K&h=ca12df68&s={SIZE}\" /> - Michel VORM<br />\n30 - <img src=\"http://bit.ly/2d8B8ov\" data-thumbnail-src=\